settings.description:
Use the Fall Away platforms to safely avoid the airship - like threats. 

Another tale from a backlog I never touch. Made sometime between August and September.
Mario's least threatening foes have come together to create insanity in the sewers.
Pick up coins from the ground, and go underground and collect them there
watch out above! due to screencrunch of the GBA, you might wanna be extra careful in jumping high in this piranha infested cavern of pipes!
If it looks too short, it's because I got up late and at this time I'm doing something else, enjoy

I spent a lot of time making this level,pls I hope you can enjoy it and bring me some support.

(also,you can give me support on the other levels that I made :v)

no scenery in the main area sadly.
either way, think you can brave this giant fortress and stop Boom Boom? for this time he's got some help!
